      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable, well-maintained vehicle that won't break the bank? This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs and drives smoothly, with solid mechanical health and a comfortable interior that shows normal wear for its age. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's a genuinely dependable daily driver that's been well cared for. A fantastic opportunity to get a quality vehicle at a fair price \u2014 come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
