    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Condition & Ready to Go! If you're looking for a well-maintained vehicle that offers real value without the premium price tag of a mint-condition car, this one is for you! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been taken care of, runs smoothly, and presents nicely both inside and out. You'll find some minor signs of normal use, as expected with any pre-owned vehicle, but nothing that affects its performance or reliability. A solid choice for anyone who wants a dependable, attractive car at a fair price! \ud83c\udf1f",
      "price": 33500.0,
