      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Stunning Mint-Condition Gem \u2013 Practically Brand New! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis is the one you've been waiting for! This vehicle is in true mint condition \u2014 meticulously cared for, spotlessly clean inside and out, and running absolutely beautifully. Every system is in top working order, the interior looks fresh and pristine, and the exterior shines like it just rolled out of the showroom. If you want a used car that genuinely delivers a like-new experience without the new-car price tag, this is your opportunity. Don't miss out \u2014 mint-condition finds like this don't last long!",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, and buyers should enter with clear, realistic expectations. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and paint that is faded or peeling in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable running condition \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or someone with mechanical skills looking for a parts car or fixer-upper. There are no claims of hidden value here; what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the car's true state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a solid, dependable choice for buyers seeking reliable transportation without the premium of a mint-condition car. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface blemishes, small stone chips, or light scratches that are consistent with normal everyday use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns to report. The interior is clean and functional, with seating surfaces showing modest wear from regular use but no major tears, stains, or damage. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs well \u2014 you can expect a smooth, confident drive. All primary systems including engine, transmission, brakes, and climate control are in good working order. This is the kind of car that a practical buyer can purchase with confidence, knowing it has been honestly represented and is ready for the road.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent so you know exactly what you're getting. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable dents, scratches, and paint fading or peeling in multiple areas. The interior is similarly worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention; it runs, but should not be considered reliable transportation without repairs. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs parts \u2014 not someone seeking a daily driver without additional investment. We're pricing it accordingly to reflect its current state honestly.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    }
